---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
    title="Services | Gecko Projects"
    description="Services - Gecko Projects offers professional consulting and project management services."
    activePage="services"
    ogUrl="https://www.gecko-projects.com/services"
>
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <section class="page-header">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Services</h1>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services Content -->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="services-detail-list">
                <div class="service-detail">
                    <h3>Virtual Assistant</h3>
                    <p>Are you trying to organise your next trip for an event, replying to agents, preparing for a meeting and supporting your team at the same time?</p>
                    <p>Let me help you to free up your time, so you can focus on your priorities!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-detail">
                    <h3>Marketing - online / offline</h3>
                    <p>You would like to be more active on social media but don't know where to go, what to post and how to reach the right audience?</p>
                    <p>Or you would like to put together a new brochure, explore a new market or review and prepare your marketing strategy, but just can't find the time? I can help.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-detail">
                    <h3>Business Development</h3>
                    <p>You know how important the follow-up is and that you should check in with your clients on a regular basis, but you simply don't have the time and energy to do it.</p>
                    <p>Let me support you in developing and maintaining client relationships and generating new leads with the intention of creating more sales/revenue.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-detail">
                    <h3>Special Projects</h3>
                    <p>You would like to tap into new areas of the business like e.g. Erasmus+ or Bildungsurlaub or increase your activity in these fields, let me take you by the hand and lead you to success.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services Highlight -->
    <section class="services-highlight">
        <div class="container">
            <p class="highlight-text">Short-term projects to long-term projects - no office space needed!</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services CTA -->
    <section class="services-cta">
        <div class="container">
            <p>Do you have other ideas and projects in mind of how we could work together?</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
